- Like Monopoly.

500
00:36:03,497 --> 00:36:07,793
Yeah, that's right.
You know I love you, baby.

501
00:36:07,835 --> 00:36:10,963
No one else means shit to me.

502
00:36:11,046 --> 00:36:14,967
I guess I must love you.
- You guess?

503
00:36:15,008 --> 00:36:20,193
