You got no choice.

664
00:50:35,953 --> 00:50:41,792
I just... I feel responsible for him.
I can't understand it.

665
00:50:42,584 --> 00:50:46,488
That's the thing about our guy. He makes
you think the opposite of what you should.

666
00:50:46,588 --> 00:50:49,074
It's a powerful thing,
being around someone so famous.

667
00:50:49,174 --> 00:50:52,574
It's like sunlight.
You wanna stay in it.

668
00:51:14,575 --> 00:51:16,268
Hey.

669
00:51:16,368 --> 00:51:20,522
