Those damn Pistons,

672
00:51:26,295 --> 00:51:28,405
they should be lined up and shot.

673
00:51:28,505 --> 00:51:32,259
We'll get it back.
We'll get it next time.

674
00:51:32,342 --> 00:51:35,954
