683
00:52:04,416 --> 00:52:07,403
Is this like another one
of Ron's great ideas?

684
00:52:07,503 --> 00:52:12,263
It ain't an idea.
It's just a thought, Paulie, a thought.

685
00:52:13,592 --> 00:52:17,587
Pete, this is all getting
to be too much for me.

686
00:52:19,056 --> 00:52:22,116
I can't handle it.
The pressure of...

687
00:52:23,268 --> 00:52:26,313
Look, nothing bothers you.

688
00:52:26,355 --> 00:52:28,757
You know, I'm not like that.
- Oh, yeah?

689
00:52:28,857 --> 00:52:31,677
